		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I found that the easiest way to get nestest working is to start from scratch, implement the opcodes as it needs it, and then compare the dumps with other emus or so, see where the path begins to differ, if the path differs by one or 2 instruction because of nmi happening earlier or something, then don't worry about that yet, just make sure you get the behaviors right, that is, the rom branches to the proper place.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
